  "title": "Business Development Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles and Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><strong>1. Cultivate Relationship Management</strong></p><p>• Prospecting for new accounts using various sales approaches.</p><p>• Identifying and pursing new business opportunities to increase</p><p>revenue and expand the customer base.</p><p>• Cultivate and maintain strong relationships with new clients,</p><p>understanding their business objectives and preferences.</p><p><strong>2. Onboard Suppliers as Strategic Partners</strong></p><p>• Collaborate with procurement teams to identify and onboard new</p><p>suppliers as strategic partners.</p><p>• Work closely with suppliers to ensure seamless integration into our</p><p>supply chain and enhance variety and quality of our product/service</p><p>offerings.</p><p><strong>3. Account Planning And Strategy</strong></p><p>• Developing and implementing account plans aligned with both the</p><p>client and our Company’s business goals</p><p>• Identifying and pursuing opportunities for upselling and cross selling of</p><p>our diverse offerings.</p><p>• Assisting clients in planning pantry selection, events and selecting</p><p>pop-up or catering menus for their pantry needs.</p><p><strong>4. Cross Functional Collaboration</strong></p><p>• Collaborating closely with internal departments to ensure seamless</p><p>delivery of products/services to key accounts.</p><p>• Provide valuable feedback to internal teams based on client’s needs</p><p>and market trends</p><p><strong>5. Performance Analysis</strong></p><p>• Monitor key account metrics and provide weekly reports to assess</p><p>effectiveness of account strategies.</p><p>• Analyse data to identify trends and proactively address any</p><p>challenges or opportunities.</p>",
